该游戏在不同平台上评分有较大差异，但商业上取得了较大的成功。[[NPD集团|NPD集团]]将其评为2003年4月第一周销量第三好的美国游戏，到月末还维持在全美第7的水平<ref name=debut>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20041120072747/http://www.gamespot.com/pc/strategy/commandconquergenerals/news_6025228.html |url=http://www.gamespot.com:80/pc/strategy/commandconquergenerals/news_6025228.html |title=Weekly PC game sales chart |date=April 16, 2003 |author=Colayco, Bob |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |archivedate=2004-11-20 |access-date=October 15, 2018 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。平均零售价为30美元<ref name=april2003>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040824011413/http://www.gamespot.com/pc/action/deltaforceblackhawkdown/news_6028850.html |url=http://www.gamespot.com:80/pc/action/deltaforceblackhawkdown/news_6028850.html |title=NPD PC sales chart |date=May 23, 2003 |author=Parker, Sam |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |archivedate=2004-08-24 |access-date=October 15, 2018 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name=lastweek>{{cite web |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20040731202646/http://www.gamespot.com/news/2003/05/29/news_6029134.html |url=http://www.gamespot.com:80/news/2003/05/29/news_6029134.html |title=NPD weekly PC game sales chart |author=Calvert, Justin |date=May 29, 2003 |archivedate=2004-07-31 |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |access-date=October 15, 2018 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

